_sText: This map is very fun. Must download. Everything is custom by me Ew_Map! Lots of hard work put into this one. 24 player spawns each equipped with 1 flash bang, 1 smoke grenade, knife and full ammo with the scout. You will enjoy this and so will your server visitors and regulars. Im new at adding my maps to fpsb so plz excuse me if the description isnt to par. I put a joint and some dank nuggets in the tool box for you bud smokers out there! looks awsome!
